casebody.head_matter:
Donald J. TRUMP, President of the United States, et al., petitioners,
v.
HAWAII, et al.
No. 17-965.
Supreme Court of the United States
Jan. 19, 2018.
The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit granted. In addition to the questions presented by the petition, the parties are directed to brief and argue Question 3 presented by the brief in opposition.
